➤ Hell Truth Website - https://www.helltruth.com
➤ Is the Devil in Charge of Hell? - https://www.amazingfacts.org/media-library/study-guide/e/4988/t/is-the-devil-in-charge-of-hell-

Where is hell? What is hell? Does it burn forever? Is the devil really in charge of it? Wait ... is hell even real? The truth about hell is going to amaze you!

It's the Bible subject that strikes fear into the heart of billions of people around the globe. In fact, many people believe it's one of the main reasons why people reject the Bible and become atheists. But the fact is—what most people believe and teach about hell is wrong. Rob Bell's picture of hell and the viral video 23 Minutes in Hell by Bill Wiese certainly have a lot to say about the reality of hell ... but what does the Bible have to say? What you believe about hell matters, because it reflects what you think about God's character and His love. We believe hell is real ... but what is its true purpose? Watch this video and then get all your questions answered at the website http://www.helltruth.com. There you'll learn about spirits in hell, the rich man in Lazarus, everlasting and unquenchable fire, and much more.
